   M /trunk/Tokenize/FilterUtils.cpp
   M /trunk/Utils/DocumentInfo.cpp
   M /trunk/Utils/DocumentInfo.h

Filters may return any field, those not recognized will be added to documents
as foreign fields. Fields with name "id" are assumed to be foreign keys to be
indexed with prefix Q, following the convention used by Xapian.
Fixed XapianIndex::removeCommonTerms().

